title: How to Dance an Advanced Cha-Cha Routine | Cha-Cha Dance

json.text: Aaron: Here again with Dance Times Square in New York City. Today, we're going to be
taking some of the cha-cha moves that you've seen in this series so far, and we're going
to be showing you where we eventually take those to. So without any further ado, we're
going to throw on some music and just get to it.
